## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of recent data and the scope of the sources reviewed. Some sources may not reflect the most current trends in juvenile delinquency. Additionally, the complexity of juvenile crime means that not all contributing factors can be fully explored in this brief report. Further research is needed to understand the interplay of these factors in different contexts and populations.

